# Format identical to .dockerignore. Reduces deploy image size.

# === Huge local-only data (the real culprits, ~10GB) ===
.local
.git
.github
attached_assets
downloads
screenshots

# === Build caches (regenerated, not needed at runtime) ===
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/.cache
**/.vite
**/.expo
**/coverage
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# === IDE / OS junk ===
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/.DS_Store
**/*.log

# === Native mobile build (iOS/Android not served by Replit) ===
artifacts/rescueat/ios
artifacts/rescueat/android
artifacts/rescueat/dist-cap
artifacts/rescueat/store-assets

# === Misc heavy files ===
*.mov
*.mp4
*.pdf
meishi.html
threat_model.md
